Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.03,0:01:37.45,Episode Title,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1022,1)}an"What I Can Do For You"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:44.24,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for laying your hands on my kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.92,0:01:51.71,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to repay you a bit for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.79,0:01:55.70,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Have you come to take me down yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.16,0:01:58.66,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin Toujou?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:28.30,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.85,0:02:35.42,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I guess I have lost my edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.20,0:02:37.73,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.44,0:02:45.01,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I thought you were the kind \Nof scum that sat back and schemed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.84,0:02:51.02,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to be \Nsuch a brave young man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.41,0:02:52.36,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.31,0:02:58.24,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Most of all, you have good eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:03.78,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, looks like the rot lies elsewhere, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:10.12,Italics,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Jin Toujou?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.12,0:03:13.64,Italics,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,His renown as a war god isn't just idle talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.75,0:03:16.17,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:33.12,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, I guess that's the Demon \NLord's weapon for you, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.56,0:03:38.57,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Devour him, Loki! Donoue's
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.51,0:03:50.96,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Wha—?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.70,0:04:03.00,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Leohart-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.22,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,Are you safe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.22,0:04:06.29,Main,Mob,0000,0000,0000,,You fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.12,0:04:08.07,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:09.72,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,He's not someone any of you can fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:40.65,Main,Leohart,0000,0000,0000,,Jin Toujou...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.32,0:04:54.27,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:01.34,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,No, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:17.65,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:19.89,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,A morning breakfast with \Na perverted woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.42,0:05:21.40,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,How invigorating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.40,0:05:23.40,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.40,0:05:26.55,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Sorry for the wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:29.68,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:32.88,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,A soft-shelled-turtle stew, \Nstewed in soft-shelled-turtle drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.88,0:05:34.00,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Since you have a sports festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:36.81,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,you need to get build \Nup your vitality!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.17,0:05:39.85,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, how did it come to that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:42.74,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, I want to see it in person, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:44.82,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, I want you to let me in!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.82,0:05:47.52,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,This house arrest has made me antsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:50.08,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, a sports festival!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.08,0:05:52.20,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think it is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:56.28,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:57.58,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,At what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:06:01.88,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect you to be the type who'd \Njoin the executive committee for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:03.99,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you volunteered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:06.22,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's true. Why did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:13.10,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it might be nice to try \Nleading a normal school life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:22.63,Missing SIgn,,0000,0000,0000,,Sports Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.61,0:06:33.58,Sign,,0000,0000,0000,,School Paper
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:32.28,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.57,0:06:42.64,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,Toujou?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.64,0:06:45.25,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? You look red.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:47.88,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:50.88,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,Umm, Hasegawa-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.29,0:06:55.14,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Tachibana. How's your body doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.14,0:06:59.08,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right. Lately I've been doing very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.08,0:07:00.76,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,It's thanks to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.76,0:07:03.15,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,I see. That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.00,0:07:09.65,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,Then, both of you, good luck \Npreparing for the sports festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:22.12,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,What was that about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.48,0:07:25.63,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Toujou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.63,0:07:27.67,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:33.06,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,You know, actually, I became \Na member of the committee
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.06,0:07:35.92,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,because Hasegawa-sensei recommended me to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.80,0:07:41.38,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,She said those with weaker bodies \Nshould enjoy it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.38,0:07:44.56,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that's a nice way of thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:48.69,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,So I really want to make it a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:50.00,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:52.82,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do our best, Tachibana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:54.56,Main,Tachibana,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:57.08,Main,Dounoue,0000,0000,0000,,You, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.30,0:08:02.24,Main,Dounoue,0000,0000,0000,,Quit complaining so much over \Nadding a firework or two!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.24,0:08:04.10,Main,Kajiura,0000,0000,0000,,The budget is limited.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:05.71,Main,Kajiura,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just order extra on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:09.63,Main,Dounoue,0000,0000,0000,,If you're on the committee, \Nthen figure something out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.17,Main,Kajiura,0000,0000,0000,,No means no!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:14.82,Main,Dounoue,0000,0000,0000,,I quit! I quit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:18.22,Main,Dounoue,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we just run this whole\N sports festival into the ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:21.23,Main,Dounoue,0000,0000,0000,,Then there wouldn't be any \Nneed to worry about a budget!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.23,0:08:22.27,Main,Dounoue,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.28,0:08:25.67,Main,Kajiura,0000,0000,0000,,Donoue-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:28.86,Main,Dounoue,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:33.61,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop there, Donoue-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.97,0:08:35.61,Main,Dounoue,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:40.37,Main,Dounoue,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:43.93,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, calm down, Donoue, Toujou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:46.88,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,If you have an opinion, then talk it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.19,0:08:48.13,Main,Dounoue,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.62,0:08:51.45,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,You're awfully noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.45,0:08:52.09,Main,Dounoue,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.99,0:09:06.17,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,If you're dissatisfied \Nwith your life at school,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.17,0:09:07.63,Main,Hasegawa,0000,0000,0000,,then I'll listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:08.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.96,0:09:09.87,Main,Dounoue,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:18.18,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have a moment, Toujou?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.18,0:09:18.66,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.48,0:09:33.07,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not trying to lecture you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.07,0:09:34.89,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.71,0:09:38.05,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not right to lay \Nyour hand on him there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.40,0:09:38.93,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.18,0:09:42.69,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, just leave Donoue's gang to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.69,0:09:43.62,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:45.42,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Toujou...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.42,0:09:47.80,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out for Hasegawa-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:48.94,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:53.52,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,She's beautiful, intelligent, \Nand a nice teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:56.19,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand why you \Nmight space out around her,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:09:59.97,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,but unfortunately in this world,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.97,0:10:03.10,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,being good and proper isn't \Nenough to make you liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:06.71,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,That's why people always \Nhave someone who hates them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.23,0:10:10.23,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Yet Hasegawa-sensei doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:12.44,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone likes her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:14.44,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:19.09,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,It's as though she's using some kind of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.85,0:10:25.18,Main,Kajiura,0000,0000,0000,,Sakasaki-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:27.48,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm? What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.48,0:10:29.85,Main,Kajiura,0000,0000,0000,,I got a hold of the fireworks shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.09,0:10:33.36,Main,Kajiura,0000,0000,0000,,When I explained the situation, \Nthey said they'd see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.36,0:10:39.24,Main,Takigawa,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.98,0:10:55.77,Flashback,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want Takigawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.77,0:10:58.90,Flashback,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you were returning \Nto the demon realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.90,0:10:59.71,Flashback,Takigawa,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:04.96,Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,but before that, I wanted \Nto give you all a warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:06.97,Flashback,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,A warning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.06,Flashback,Takigawa,0000,0000,0000,,About Basacchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:13.64,Flashback,Takigawa,0000,0000,0000,,A while back I made Naruse's power \Ngo out of control during battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.64,0:11:15.75,Flashback,Takigawa,0000,0000,0000,,and Basacchi saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:19.91,Flashback,Takigawa,0000,0000,0000,,However, if Basacchi's power were \Nforced to go out of control,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:22.32,Flashback,Takigawa,0000,0000,0000,,could you two save him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.63,0:11:23.82,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,I—!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:26.68,Flashback,Takigawa,0000,0000,0000,,If you feel even a little responsibility,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.68,0:11:28.76,Flashback,Takigawa,0000,0000,0000,,then at least get stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.76,0:11:32.33,Flashback,Takigawa,0000,0000,0000,,At least strong enough to kill \Nhim if it ever comes down to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:35.04,Flashback,Takigawa,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.07,0:11:57.27,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,We need to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.28,0:11:59.36,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.43,0:12:12.37,Main,Kajiura,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Toujou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.20,Main,Kajiura,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't mean to keep you this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:16.15,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.15,0:12:17.68,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:19.88,Main,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Then take care on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.20,0:12:21.02,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.50,0:12:30.57,Italics,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,In a moment, the special express will \Nbe passing through on track two.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:35.77,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,A barrier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:39.91,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.23,0:12:47.95,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Are they being controlled?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.09,0:12:52.05,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Magic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.05,0:12:52.79,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:55.04,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,The barrier?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.16,0:12:58.60,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,If I avoid them...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.44,0:13:08.30,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to deal with them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:12.27,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.40,0:13:16.94,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I can't take them all—!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:20.76,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.30,0:13:25.54,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see what happened when \Nthis barrier suddenly went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.09,0:13:28.07,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.56,0:13:36.88,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Those people are being controlled!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.88,0:13:38.49,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm holding back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.49,0:13:39.84,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't take me for a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:49.22,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Now we just need to erase their \Nmemories of us, and we're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.52,0:13:52.43,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.32,0:13:56.68,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Because of the report Yuki \Nmade to the village...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.16,0:14:00.89,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,They thought Onee wasn't enough to \Nhandle observing things on her own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:03.78,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,So they dispatched an extra member.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.78,0:14:05.98,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.98,0:14:07.08,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.08,0:14:09.38,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I came for Onee's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.38,0:14:11.95,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Not for you or Naruse Mio!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:13.62,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:18.60,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Still, Basara, don't you have any \Nidea who might want to target you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.27,0:14:23.63,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I felt some faint, unknown waves \Ncoming from your school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:25.13,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.88,0:14:31.89,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.01,0:14:35.80,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Mio? Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:36.80,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Onee!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:58.73,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.00,0:15:01.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mio?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:02.82,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Onee?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.92,0:15:11.68,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Surprise! It's a big success!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:15.35,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Maria, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.35,0:15:17.61,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, pardon me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.12,0:15:22.00,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:23.69,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,You two?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.83,0:15:48.71,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.72,0:16:00.35,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.18,0:16:05.72,Main,Mio,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:12.48,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,The Master-Servant pact?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:17.09,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, all that just now was \Nto deepen your Master-Servant bond
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:19.72,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,with Basara and raise your combat prowess?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.20,0:16:20.97,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:26.08,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Since Mio and I both became \Nbitches and submitted to Basara,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.08,0:16:28.13,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,all three of us have grown stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:30.85,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We talked it over together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:33.95,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Training and practice \Nisn't enough on its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:38.18,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We agreed we need to do everything \Nwe can to grow stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.58,0:16:41.12,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,So we decided to submit to Basara even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.87,0:16:44.08,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,We wanted to deepen our bond of trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.56,0:16:48.75,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,So then Maria suggested this would be best.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:54.34,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, we both became bitches.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.34,0:16:55.64,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.64,0:16:57.47,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you \Nwanted to be stronger,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.47,0:16:59.59,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,relying on the magic of demons \Nand doing things like—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.16,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,It's crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.16,0:17:05.08,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,If Yuki hadn't forged a \NMaster-Servant pact with Basara,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:09.96,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,then it's likely we all would've died \Nduring the fight against Zolgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.97,0:17:14.25,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Would you have preferred that, Kurumi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.25,0:17:15.70,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's—
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:17.53,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Stop that, Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:20.47,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumi doesn't know about our circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:26.74,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.74,0:17:28.68,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it was too \Nstimulating for the little kid
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.68,0:17:32.67,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,who knows absolutely nothing about these things \Nor the delicacies between men and women,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.67,0:17:37.18,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,so she's just getting annoyingly angry \Nwith us to hide her own embarrassment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.18,0:17:39.27,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't treat me like a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:42.88,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an adult who matured earlier than Onee!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:44.98,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,My breasts have grown bigger, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.98,0:17:46.50,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm a match for her size!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:51.97,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,You say you're more mature than Yuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:54.51,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, then \Nwhy don't you prove it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.86,0:17:57.84,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,P-Prove it? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.84,0:18:01.39,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You aren't sure about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.39,0:18:02.87,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.87,0:18:05.77,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Fine! I'll prove I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.11,0:18:09.52,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Now, confirm it for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.95,0:18:11.42,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Right away, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:12.82,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.18,0:18:16.03,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:18.68,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.68,0:18:21.32,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:26.04,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.66,0:18:29.88,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I just gave you a little \Nbit of a succubus's baptism
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.88,0:18:32.62,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,and put you in a state of arousal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.06,0:18:34.24,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Basara-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:34.76,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.76,0:18:39.40,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Please confirm whether Kurumi-san really \Nis more mature than Yuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:44.00,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Right now Kurumi-san is just \Nas aroused as Yuki-san gets
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:45.88,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,when the Master-Servant \Npact's curse activates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:49.36,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.36,0:18:51.39,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,If it's the same as Yuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.78,0:18:54.32,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,then I have to make her submit, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.69,0:18:55.68,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.68,0:18:59.77,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,However, please let Yuki-san do it, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:04.83,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she can't abide having her little \Nsister claim she's more mature, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.07,0:19:06.08,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:12.48,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're cheeky for a little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:15.48,Main,Yuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you which of us is more mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:17.46,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,No! Onee?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.93,0:19:20.69,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,No, you can't! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:23.89,Main,Kurumi,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:27.42,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, Kurumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:29.99,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,We'll relieve you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.32,0:19:42.74,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:47.26,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you make Kurumi go \Nthat far when we haven't
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.12,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,forged a Master-Servant pact?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:50.52,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.28,0:19:55.08,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would be better \Nfor Kurumi-san to learn
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:58.00,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,what the Master-Servant pact \Nyou all share was like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:02.12,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,But that doesn't mean you needed \Nto play the villain on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.30,0:20:07.89,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,I have an older sister, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.65,0:20:10.96,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,My strict older sister
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.96,0:20:14.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,probably won't forgive the actions \NI took during the incident with Zolgia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.15,0:20:20.68,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,So, at the very least, I wanted Yuki-san \Nand Kurumi-san to remain friendly sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.92,0:20:25.30,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.24,0:20:27.17,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:31.48,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Basara, you have such a thing for little girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:32.55,Main,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.36,0:20:35.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I just cherish you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.84,Main,Maria,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.62,0:20:53.28,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Somewhere here, there's an enemy after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.68,0:20:59.23,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,A frightening one that holds the \Npower to manipulate other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:03.07,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,Who on earth...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:07.12,Flashback,Sakazaki,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out for Hasegawa-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.67,0:21:14.28,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,No, it doesn't matter who I'm up against.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.32,0:21:17.25,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,They're all my precious family.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:24.84,Italics,Basara,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect them for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.57,0:23:18.70,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,We got swept awfully far away.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.80,0:23:25.04,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,There, there. You're a fortunate boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.63,0:23:28.09,Main,Jin,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
